In the 1960s, Bruce McLaren and Denny Hulme became indomitable forces in racing at the wheel of the potent M1A, but the only way to extend McLaren’s magic to customer racers was to join forces with Elva Cars. The result paved the way for McLaren’s global success in both Can-Am racing and road cars. ​

Today, the McLaren Elva pays homage to that rich racing history…​

​
@mclarenbeverlyhills 
#McLaren #McLarenElva #Elva

McLaren Special Operations today unveils the ‘Albert’ Speedtail, a bespoke commission by @mclarenbeverlyhills. ‘Albert’ is an homage to the first Speedtail attribute testing prototype from 2018 with one of the most complex paint themes ever completed by MSO. ​

The exterior design reflects the aerodynamic prowess of the McLaren Speedtail with beautifully painted lines representing the optimised airflow over the car. ​

#McLaren #Speedtail #MSO

node.text: Pictured in action on circuit at Silverstone the @pirelli_motorsport Hot Lap experience saw the 720S showcase its breadth of ability. #Supercar #Pirelli #PirelliHotLaps

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McLaren Automotive on September 10, 2021. May be an image of car.

node.text: Bespoke carbon fibre bodywork. Pared-back minimalist design. Advanced aerodynamics. All combine to ensure that power, speed and exacting poise are unrelenting. #765LTSpider #McLaren #Supercar

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by McLaren Automotive on September 10, 2021 tagging @pirelli. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: The 765LT Spider is alive with driver-focused engineering and technology. A dynamic balance that thrills. Bespoke Pirelli P Zero™ Trofeo R tyres take cornering speeds to new heights. A revised brake booster and unique pad material make pedal feel and stopping power simply incredible. #765LTSpider #McLaren #Supercar

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McLaren Automotive on September 10, 2021. May be an image of car and road.

node.text:
The bespoke carbon fibre body panels, rear bodywork mesh and glazing look breathtaking on the 765LT Spider. Their functional performance is equally impressive. They comprise 20kg of the overall 80kg weight saving. And deliver 25% more downforce. 

#765LTSpider #McLaren #Supercar

#McLaren720SSpider #720SSpider #McLarenAdventures

#McLaren720SSpider #720SSpider #McLarenAdventures
